# ğŸ§  GitMate â€” AI Git Terminal Assistant

GitMate is a terminal-based assistant powered by **LangChain + your choice of LLM (Gemini, OpenAI, Claude)**.  
It helps you execute Git and shell commands interactively, detects common errors like merge conflicts or fatal errors, and offers AI-powered help â€” right inside your terminal.

