## âš™ï¸ Features

- ğŸ’¬ Talk to the AI with `@bot your question`
- ğŸ§  Pick your preferred model: OpenAI GPT-4o, Gemini 2.0, or Claude 3
- ğŸ¤– Auto-detect Git errors and offer intelligent help
- ğŸ’¾ Logs the entire terminal session
- âš¡ Fully automated mode with CLI flags (`--model`, `--api-key`)

---

## ğŸš€ Quickstart

### 1. Install

```bash
pip install gitmate-ai
````

### 2. Run Interactively

```bash
gitmate
```

You'll be prompted to select an LLM model and enter your API key.

---

## ğŸ”§ Command-Line Arguments

| Flag        | Description                              | Example            |
| ----------- | ---------------------------------------- | ------------------ |
| `--model`   | Select LLM: `openai`, `gemini`, `claude` | `--model gemini`   |
| `--api-key` | Provide your API key                     | `--api-key sk-...` |

Skip all prompts:

```bash
gitmate --model claude --api-key YOUR_KEY
```

